Object.Field:
This options allows adding or overriding Hadoop configuration properties.

E.g.

{
'hbase.zookeeper.quorum': 'HOST',
'hbase.mapreduce.inputtable': 'TAB'
}

To specify file path for hadoopRDD and newAPIHadoopRDD sources, use values such as 

{"mapreduce.input.fileinputformat.inputdir":"/tmp/mydir/QA_datafile.txt"}
